title: Group Therapy: Her HOA Yells At Her All the Time
description: Lisa is calling in with an issue she's having with her HOA.  Her and her husband have gotten in trouble for not mowing their lawn enough, leaving a Little Tikes basketball hoop in the yard, and always leaving their boat out.  She thinks they're out to get her or is she in the wrong?
